trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving"></xref> event of a <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerer metoden som håndterer den <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving"> </xref> hendelse for en <xref href="System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The ProfileAutoSaveEventHandler delegate is defined for the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class.
trans-unit.target: Representanten ProfileAutoSaveEventHandler er definert for <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>hendelsen for <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klasse.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>

trans-unit.source: You can access the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> class in the Global.asax file for your ASP.NET application, as shown in the example for this topic.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>hendelsen til den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>klasse i filen Global.asax for ASP.NET-programmet, som vist i eksemplet for dette emnet.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event is raised at the end of page execution if the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A> property is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>hendelsen skjer på slutten av siden kjøring hvis den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileManager.AutomaticSaveEnabled%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A> method automatically determines whether properties that are made up of primitive types, strings, or <xref:System.DateTime> objects have been changed, by checking the <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue.IsDirty%2A> property value for each <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue> in the user profile.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A>metoden automatisk bestemmer om egenskaper som er består av primitive typer, strenger, eller <xref:System.DateTime>objekter har blitt endret av kontroll av <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue.IsDirty%2A>egenskapsverdien for hver <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue>profilen.</xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue> </xref:System.Configuration.SettingsPropertyValue.IsDirty%2A> </xref:System.DateTime> </xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: However, the <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A> method cannot explicitly determine whether a custom class has changed.
trans-unit.target: Imidlertid den <xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A>metoden eksplisitt kan ikke avgjøre om en egendefinert klasse er endret.</xref:System.Configuration.SettingsBase.Save%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can handle the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event to determine whether a custom object has been modified and to continue with the automatic save for modified objects and cancel the automatic save if no objects have been modified.
trans-unit.target: Du kan behandle den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>-hendelsen for å finne ut om et egendefinert objekt er endret og for å fortsette med automatisk lagring for endrede objekter og avbryte automatisk hvis ingen objekter er endret.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>

trans-unit.source: To cancel the automatic profile save operation, set the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property to `false` in the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event; otherwise, set the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil avbryte automatisk profilen lagringen, kan du angi den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>egenskapen `false` i den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>hendelsen; ellers satt i <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>egenskapen `true`.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>

trans-unit.source: There may be multiple subscribers to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event.
trans-unit.target: Det kan være flere abonnenter i <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule> will use the last value that the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property is set to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>vil bruke sist verdien som den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>er satt til.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule>

trans-unit.source: As a result, it is recommended that you explicitly set the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A> property in the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> event, regardless of whether you are canceling or continuing with the automatic save, as you may need to overwrite the value set by an earlier subscriber.
trans-unit.target: Resultatet anbefales det at du har angitt den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>egenskap i den <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving>hendelse, uansett om du avbryter eller fortsetter automatisk lagring, som du må kanskje overskrive verdien som er angitt av en tidligere abonnenten.</xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileModule.ProfileAutoSaving> </xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileAutoSaveEventArgs.ContinueWithProfileAutoSave%2A>
